thread.title: Nigel Hedges
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Nigel Hedges

author: Nigel Hedges
title: Nigel Hedges
text: I was able to find what I was looking for on the site really quickly which was ace, then almost made a change of heart before returning back to my original pre-order...all without losing my cart, because some sites bug out like that. After I ordered I received the right amount of emails acknowledging my order and tracking. It got delivered earlier than anticipated (not something you should expect, but it was a pleasant surprise). Very happy with the product too. So a good ordering experience from me.
